author: VR Gorilla - Virtual Reality & 360 Videos
description:
Join us on a journey through Iceland’s colorful capital. From Hallgrímskirkja and Rainbow Street to peaceful lakes and seaside art. Then, leave the city behind as we head into the wild landscapes of Hvalfjörður to reach Glymur, one of Iceland’s tallest and most stunning waterfalls.
